  <brief_title>Continue Entecavir Rollover From China</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of the Safety and Antiviral Activity of Open-Label Entecavir (BMS-200475) in Adults With Chronic Hepatitis B Infection Who Have Completed Dosing in a Previous Phase II/III Study in China</official_title>
  <sponsors>
