    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine if treatment with entecavir is safe and well
      tolerated in patients who completed dosing in a previous entecavir study in China, but are
      requiring further treatment of their chronic hepatitis B virus infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
